Class LaundryItem

java.lang.Object
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.LaundryItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
CleaningStyle
Direct Known Subclasses:
DryClean, WetClean
public abstract class LaundryItem extends Object implements CleaningStyle
Represents a laundry item in an order. Each laundry item has a type, quantity, price, notes, and an assigned employee for processing. This is an abstract class that defines common properties for specific laundry items such as dry cleaning or wet cleaning. Implements the CleaningStyle interface.
Version:
23.0
Author:
Ferhat Kasim Koc
